[MUSIC - FUN HOME, "IT ALL COMES
 BACK"]

00:12:19.488 --> 00:15:26.569
[SINGING "IT ALL COMES BACK"]

00:15:26.569 --> 00:15:30.830
BETH MALONE: Caption--
every so often, there

00:15:30.830 --> 00:15:34.950
was a rare moment
of perfect balance

00:15:34.950 --> 00:15:39.135
when I soared above him.

