00:34:18.530 --> 00:34:22.620
So it sort of loves to make
you think you know how it works

00:34:22.620 --> 00:34:24.540
and then switch
the rules on you,

00:34:24.540 --> 00:34:27.031
which is kind of-- the
thing about memories

00:34:27.031 --> 00:34:28.739
