like, oh, yeah, that,

00:34:28.739 --> 00:34:30.949
and sometimes you're like, what?

00:34:30.949 --> 00:34:32.510
Oh, yeah.

00:34:32.510 --> 00:34:34.159
Oh, wow, that.

00:34:34.159 --> 00:34:36.080
So the memories
don't come at you

00:34:36.080 --> 00:34:38.850
and behave the same way from
memory to memory or moment

00:34:38.850 --> 00:34:41.160
to moment in this play.

